snippet.title: Thinkin' Science: ZAP! (1998) PC Gameplay
snippet.description:
This video has had to be Reuploaded to remove the microphone sounds.

Thinkin' Science: ZAP! is an educational game for first and second graders created by Edmark Corporation in 1998.
